Original content and influencer social media campaigns by Zalando which has
    obviously well understood how to tap into the ubiquitous narratives of
    self-expression and authenticity to sell clothes people can use to "be
    themselves".
I always want to be different, at least a little bit.

Just wearing it in a way that just feels free and easy. So you feel [...]
    like you are expressing yourself in a way that feels right and true to you.

I feel free when I get to do what I want. It's really important to me to
    express myself and dare to be myself.

I create music and art because I can't help it. [...] it's so great to
    create something beautiful out of nothing.

I wear what I want to express. [...] just own it, it makes everything in
    life easier.
